<div id="pf4468" class="pf w4f h303" data-page-no="4468"><div class="pc pc4468 w4f h303"><div class="t m256 x92 h6c y2ea0 ff1 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">LESSON 8 August 19-25 </div><div class="t m302 x16 h6c y2af ff1 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Ananias went his way, and entered </div><div class="t mb98 x92 h6c y2069 ff1 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">into the house; and putting his hands </div><div class="t m3b0 x92 h6c y4fa ff1 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">on him [Saul] said, Brother Saul, the </div><div class="t m7db x92 h6c ybec ff1 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Lord, even Jesus, that appeared unto </div><div class="t ma87 x92 h6c y778 ff1 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">thee in the way as thou camest, hath </div><div class="t ma07 x92 h6c y100f ff1 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">sent me, that thou mightest receive </div><div class="t m96 x92 h6c yaaa ff1 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">thy sight, and be filled with the Holy </div><div class="t mbc x92 h6c y53c ff1 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Ghost&quot; (Acts 9:17). </div><div class="t m111 x71 h35 y39e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">As soon as Saul surrendered to the </div><div class="t m13a x92 h35 ya73 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">power of Jesus and wanted to be His </div><div class="t m210 x15 h35 y569 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">disciple, Ananias was sent to him with </div><div class="t me12 x15 h35 y18f6 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the instruction to pray for the new </div><div class="t ma55 x15 h35 y363 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">disciple to be filled with the Holy </div><div class="t m10a x15 h35 y7b0 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Spirit. &quot;The Lord ... hath sent me, that </div><div class="t me8a x15 h35 y496 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">thou mightest . . . be filled with the </div><div class="t m122c x15 h35 yf7e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Holy Ghost.&quot; </div><div class="t m9ce x71 h35 yef7 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The plan of God is that every </div><div class="t m3d0 x15 h35 y8bc ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">disciple should receive the fullness of </div><div class="t m1168 x15 h35 y79a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the Spirit, reaching that mature stage </div><div class="t ma74 x15 h35 y120d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">where it may be said that he or she is </div><div class="t m8fe x15 h35 y59f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">filled with the Spirit. </div><div class="t m61a x71 h35 y76f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">In this lesson we plan to review the </div><div class="t m8f9 x15 h35 ya79 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">different stages in the work of the </div><div class="t m1a18 x15 h35 y40a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Spirit and in our relationship with </div><div class="t mde3 x15 h35 y476 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Him. We shall study what the Spirit of </div><div class="t m6f3 x27 h35 yaf5 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God does on our behalf in each one of </div><div class="t m234 x15 h35 y2ea ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">those aspects of His work. </div><div class="t mf2 x26 h35 y8d9 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Speaking about Christ, John says: </div><div class="t m69a x27 h35 yabc ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;God giveth not the Spirit by measure </div><div class="t mbe0 x27 h35 y1206 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">unto him&quot; (John 3:34). Christ, as the </div><div class="t m6d4 x27 h35 y307 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Second Person of the Godhead, and </div><div class="t m2ee x27 h35 y78a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">being Himself God, did not need the  </div><div class="t m58b xbc h35 y88f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Holy Spirit. But, in order to give us an </div><div class="t m123 x21 h35 yc6a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">example as a human being, He was </div><div class="t m9b5 x21 h35 y137a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">filled with the Spirit. This was visibly </div><div class="t m87c x21 h35 y71b ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">evident at His baptism. Just as God did </div><div class="t m745 x21 h35 y8d3 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">not give His Spirit &quot;by measure,&quot; that </div><div class="t m2c7 x21 h35 y1010 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">is to say, sparingly, to the Son of man, </div><div class="t m179 x21 h35 y1609 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">so He does not give the Spirit sparingly </div><div class="t m3cb x21 h35 y377 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to His children. </div><div class="t m7b0 x4b h35 y9d8 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">It is the privilege of every one of us </div><div class="t m1a18 x21 h35 y388 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to make room for the Holy Spirit to </div><div class="t m610 x21 h35 y15ec ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">operate in his or her life. In this lesson </div><div class="t mac8 x21 h35 y2dc ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">we shall seek to make clear how this </div><div class="t m1ad x21 h35 ya12 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">takes place. </div><div class="t mddf x70 h6c y85d ff1 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">DAILY HIGHLIGHTS </div><div class="t m7a0 x21 h6c y666 ff1 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. </div><div class="t m167a x78 h6c y666 ff1 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Convicting Power </div><div class="t m1127 x78 h6c yf7d ff1 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(John 16:8) </div><div class="t mec2 x21 h6c yef7 ff1 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t m4d2 x7b h6c yef7 ff1 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Indwelling Power </div><div class="t m1081 x78 h6c y8bc ff1 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(John 14:16, 17) </div><div class="t m2ca x21 h6c y79a ff1 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t m4c3 x78 h6c y79a ff1 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Enabling Power </div><div class="t m313 x78 h6c yf ff1 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Acts 1:5) </div><div class="t mb90 x21 h6c y510 ff1 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. </div><div class="t m1e8 x78 h6c y907 ff1 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Latter Rain </div><div class="t mcfb x78 h6c y37d ff1 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Joel 2:28, 29) </div><div class="t mb90 x21 h6c ya79 ff1 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">5. </div><div class="t m31c x78 h6c y19cf ff1 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Receiving the Spirit </div><div class="t mce9 x7b h6c y40a ff1 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Luke 11:13) </div><div class="t m9b x70 h6c y476 ff1 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">6. </div><div class="t meda x78 h6c y476 ff1 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">A Daily Experience </div><div class="t mf42 x7b h6c yaf5 ff1 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Gal. 3:14) </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
